# Playwright testing (required)

After **every code change** to this app, run Playwright tests before telling the user work is complete:

```bash
cd voice_customer_support_system
npm run test:e2e
```

Tests run on port **3099** by default (see `playwright.config.ts`). Override with `PLAYWRIGHT_PORT=3002 npm run test:e2e` to reuse another dev server.

The web app lives in `services/web/`. Playwright starts it via `npm run dev -w @voice-support/web`.

## Adding coverage for new features

When adding or changing UI behavior, add or update specs in `e2e/` so the new flow is covered.
